Input: AvailabilityRules (weekly), Exceptions (date overrides), Confirmed Appointments, Holds, lead times, buffers.
Process: Generate slots per day → remove conflicts → apply travel-time padding based on previous/next jobs using distance heuristic.
Output: Bookable slots for next N days.
Reservation: Creating a pending appointment optionally places a temporary hold with timeout (e.g., 15 min) to avoid double-booking.
Auto-expire: Pending requests not accepted in SLA window auto-cancel and release holds.